imdb.plot outline: Ill Call You is a half hour comedy/drama centered around Jon Culaine, a depressed writer who, after the destruction of a short lived marriage, attempts to navigate the perils of on-line dating in search of true love. Surrounded by a group of know-it-all friends and an imaginary therapist saboteur, who all claim to know whats best, he is misguided along a hilarious never-ending journey for a seemingly unattainable goal.
